==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pentacid
<hw>Pen*tac"id</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Pent</ets>a- + <ets>acid</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Capable of neutralizing, or combining with, five molecules of a
monobasic acid; having five hydrogen atoms capable of substitution by
acid residues; -- said of certain complex bases.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pentacle</ent>⟦br⟧
